   </teiHeader> <facsimile> <graphic url="1896_AS_RBH_3_00032.jpeg"/> <graphic url="1896_AS_RBH_3_00033.jpeg"/> <graphic url="1896_AS_RBH_3_00034.jpeg"/> <graphic url="1896_AS_RBH_3_00035.jpeg"/> </facsimile> <text type="letter"> <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_3_00032.jpeg"/><hi rend="latintype">An Dr. Rich. Beer Hofmann</hi></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_3_00034.jpeg"/><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KLM20191119-1"/><date when="1896-09-13">So<c rendition="#gemination-n"/>tag</date><note type="commentary" xml:id="KLM20191119-1h">Der <date>13. 9. 1896</date> war ein Sonntag, <rs ref="#pmb2121" type="person">Schnitzler</rs> irrt sich mit der Beschriftung »<quote><date>12/IX 96</date></quote>.</note>. – <time>½ 6. <hi rend="latintype">N. M.</hi></time></dateline></opener><p><salute>Lieber Richard, </salute>wie ka<c rendition="#gemination-n"/> man nicht einmal eine Po<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t zu Haus la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en wo man zu finden wäre! Ich ko<c rendition="#gemination-m"/>e per Rad von <rs ref="#pmb968" type="place">Mödling</rs> – <pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_3_00035.jpeg"/><rs ref="#pmb24686" type="person">Tini</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb17504" type="place">Alland</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb34343" type="place">Neuhaus</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40112" type="place">Potten<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tein</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40115" type="place">Antonsga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e 4</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb680" type="place">Franzensga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e 54</rs> –</p><p>Der Doctor <rs ref="#pmb12740" type="person">Schwarzkopf</rs> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t auch da, der grüßt Sie, aber nicht<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o herzlich wie ich.</p><closer>Ihr <signed>ArthSch</signed></closer></div></body> </text></TEI>